  <brief_title>Chemotherapy in Treating Patients With Stage IIIB or Stage IV Non-small Cell Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Gemcitabine and Vinorelbine vs Standard Chemotherapy Containing Cisplatin for Stage IIIB/IV Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer</official_title>
